name: I Love My Pet Photos
description:
Show Your LOVE For Your Pets With Our Full Color Magnets and Decals for Your Vehicles.

Email us your favorite photo of your pets in JPEG format along with names and what ever you would like to say.

Victorysignsinc@gmail.com

Choose either a Full Colored Magnet or Decal both measure 6" x 6"

$1.00 for each order goes to SPCA to care for pets waiting to be adopted.

name: Adopted Pets Pics
description:
Show your love for your pet and encourage others to look into adoption. We donate $1.00 from every order to the SPCA to care for pets waiting for a home.

Email us your favorite pet photo along with name and adoption date or anything else you would like to say in jpeg format.
victorysignsinc@gmail.com

Let us know if you would like a Magnet or Decal for your vehicle.

Magnets and Decals are 6" x 6" full color!
